svasti śrī {meykkīrtti} {end of the line missing}

kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu maṉṉupperumpaḻuvūrt tiru ‡ [t]toṟṟamuṭaiyamahādevaṟku vāṇakovaraiyaṉ cuttamallaṉ [U] ‡ tta[[maco]] ‡ ḻaṉāṉ Ilaṅkeśvara[n]eṉ I[ttevaṟ]kku tirucceṉṉa[[ṭai]][p] puṟamāka pūmi ceytu kuṭutta paric[[ā]] ‡ [vatu Ippa] ‡ ḻuvūr naka[[ra]]ttār iṭai [[nā]][ṉ] mukkaḻai[ñ] {end of the line missing}

[[llai]] mahātevi viṇṇakar āḻvār nilattukku vaṭak ‡ kum vaṭapāṟkellai Iraṇamukarāmaṉ vāykkālukku teṟkum kiḻakku cuttamali va ‡ [ti]kku me ‡ ṟkum Āka nāṉkellaikkum Uṭpaṭṭa nilam Orumā Iṉṉilam Orumāvum tirutti Itevaṟkku ‡ [tiruppa] ‡ ṭimāṟṟukku [t]evatānamāka ca {end of the line missing}
